author: vmote
msg: Remove storage of apps/FOUserAgent from fo/FONode in favor of storing it once in a higher level class (currently Driver), and accessing it from there. Cleaner design, uses less memory, at the expense of some additional processing time to come up the tree to find the information.

author: vmote
msg: Remove all storage of fo/FOInputHandler from within the FO Tree itself, in favor of storing it one time in apps/Document and getting it from there when needed. Makes everything cleaner, and uses less memory, at the probable expense of some processing time (to go up the tree to get to Document).

author: vmote
msg: move storage of ID references from fo/FOInputHandler to fo/FOTreeControl (implemented in apps/Document)

author: vmote
msg: remove some convoluted and unnecessary logic -- we already know the Document that is being processed
